children.name: Effects
children.text:
You are transformed into a beast chosen by the caster. You gain the beast's stats, including hit points and mental ability scores, bur retain your alignment and personality. If the beast's hit points drop to 0, you return to your original form with your previous hit points, and any excess damage carries over to your original form. 
You cant cast spells or take actions your new form doesnt allow. You can't speak or take any other action that requires hands or speech. You can't activate, use, wield, or otherwise benefit from any of your equipment.
